[2014-03-22] emacsshot.  Find a function for taking a screenshot of Emacs from within Emacs at https://github.com/marcowahl/emacsshot.
----
[2014-04-05] rope-reading.  A mode for genuine bidirectional reading of text by reversing every other line in the visible buffer part.  This mode depends on program 'convert' of the Image Magick-suite.  Get the latest version at https://github.com/marcowahl/reverse-every-other-line.  Comments and improvements welcome.
